---

<footer class="bg-[#00664e] text-white py-8 border-t border-white/10">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-8 text-sm leading-relaxed">

        <div class="space-y-4 lg:col-span-2">
            <a href="/" class="block">
                <img 
                    src={footerLogo.src} 
                    alt="JLO Global Resources" 
                    class="h-14 w-auto object-contain mb-2" 
                />
            </a>

            <p class="text-gray-200 text-xs max-w-sm">
                Founded in 2019, JLO Global Resources is a Petaling Jaya-based full-suite agency. We blend creativity, strategy, and technology to help businesses build strong brands.
            </p>

            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mt-4">
                <a href={xUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="group w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-white flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:bg-[#0d55a9]" aria-label="X">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 fill-slate-900 group-hover:fill-white transition-colors" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
